</P>
<P>
 Marina linebacker Steve Cooper recovered a fumbled snap by Corona del Mar 
quarterback Josh Walz to seal the victory with 18 seconds left. 
</P>
<P>
 Aron Bergman intercepted a pass from Sea King quarterback Aaron Perlmutter on 
the first play from scrimmage, and the Vikings scored three plays later, on a 
10-yard run by quarterback Matt Roberson. 
</P>
<P>
