with a one-yard touchdown run. The two-point conversion gave Marina a 22-6 
lead. 
</P>
<P>
 The Sea Kings pulled within seven when Perlmutter hit Bill Taketa for a 
42-yard touchdown, then ran in the two-point conversion. 
</P>
<P>
 Corona del Mar had a chance to tie with under a minute left, when Walz fumbled 
the snap at midfield. JON CLIFFORD 
